---
const disciplines = [
  'Fractional CTO / CAIO',
  'AI Systems & Machine Learning',
  'RAG, Agents & Automation',
  'Real-Time Graphics & GPU',
  'Audio Engineering & DSP',
  'Product Architecture',
];
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="about-grid">

    <div class="about-body">
      <p class="about-lead fade-up" data-delay="100">
        A CTO and AI builder with an unusual origin story — twenty years across art, sound, and engineering, now helping companies ship AI that actually works.
      </p>

      <p class="about-prose fade-up" data-delay="240">
        I grew up between Germany and Spain, studied in London, and have been based in Berlin since 2007. The first decade was real-time audiovisual work — graphics, audio tools, and interactive installations for galleries, opera houses, and electronic music stages. The second decade brought that into startups: leading engineering teams, owning product and architecture, and shipping AI-driven systems. Today I work as a fractional CTO/CAIO and hands-on builder — the kind of technical foundation that lets small companies move faster than they should be able to, without breaking in production.
      </p>

      <div class="about-disciplines fade-up" data-delay="360">
        <p class="about-disciplines-label">Disciplines</p>
        <ul class="disciplines-list">
          {disciplines.map(d => <li>{d}</li>)}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-meta fade-in" data-delay="480">
      <dl class="meta-list">
        <dd>Berlin, DE</dd>
        <dd class="meta-coords">52°31′ N · 13°23′ E</dd>
        <dd class="meta-sep">Open to</dd>
        <dd>AI readiness &amp; production audits</dd>
        <dd>AI build sprints</dd>
        <dd>Fractional CTO / CAIO</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule, oklch(87% 0.005 260));
    background: var(--white, oklch(99% 0 0));
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.6fr 1fr;
    gap: 0 clamp(3rem, 5vw, 6rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.2vw, 1.65rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink, oklch(10% 0.012 258));
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    max-width: 44ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .about-prose {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--dim, oklch(28% 0.010 258));
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 58ch;
  }

  .about-disciplines-label {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ghost, oklch(50% 0.006 260));
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .disciplines-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.55rem 2rem;
  }

  .disciplines-list li {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--dim, oklch(28% 0.010 258));
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  /* ── Meta sidebar ── */
  .about-meta {
    text-align: right;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .meta-list {
    list-style: none;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ghost, oklch(50% 0.006 260));
    line-height: 2.2;
  }
  .meta-list dd { margin: 0; }

  /* coordinates in a slightly more visible ghost tone */
  .meta-coords {
    color: var(--rule, oklch(87% 0.005 260));
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .meta-sep {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--cobalt, oklch(52% 0.22 265));
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .about-meta { text-align: left; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .disciplines-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
